INSTRUCTIONS:
Write a SUBSTANTIAL, DEEPLY TEXTURED section of creative non-fiction or narrative prose based on the scaffold above.
• The voice must be distinct. Use the specific author weights to guide vocabulary and rhythm.
• Avoid generic AI nature writing (e.g., "tapestry of colors", "symphony of sounds").
